≠In Loving Memory of
Terence James Donovan
15 August 1942 - 15 December 2015
Remembering you is easy, we do it everyday.
Missing you is a heartache, that never goes away."Ī
ģ"I wish I had the healing words
to wrap around the quiet,
Wish I knew some magic ways,
to lighten up your night,"
by Andrew W.S. Kenny: beautiful father, fantastic friend"∂
≥Nowhere is more loved than this treasured
place where joyous times are shared with
family, friends and all who stop to wonder al
the beauty surrounding them. Christine Kitchen."Ļ
